  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM1.8">
<l>kōlārnta neṭuñcārṅkaṅ kūṉaṟ caṅkaṅ</l>
<l>kolaiyāḻi koṭuntaṇṭu koṟṟa voḷvāḷ</l>
<l>kālārnta katikkaruṭa ṉeṉṉum veṉṟik</l>
<l>kaṭumpaṟavai yivaiyaṉaittum puṟañcūḻ kāppac</l>
<l>cēlārnta neṭuṅkaḻaṉi cōlai cūḻnta</l>
<l>tiruvaraṅkat taravaṇaiyiṟ paḷḷi koḷḷum</l>
<l>mālōṉaik kaṇṭiṉpak kalavi yeyti</l>
<l>valviṉaiyē ṉeṉṟukolō vāḻu nāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When is the day that I, with a forceful karma, will live,</l>
<l>seeing and attaining the pleasure of union with</l>
<l>Mālōṉ,  who sleeps on the serpent-bed</l>
<l rend="indent">in Śrīraṅgam surrounded by groves [and] large paddy fields filled with carp,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the long Śārṅga abounding with arrows, the fine curved conch,</l>
<l rend="indent">the murderous discus, the cruel club, the sword glowing with victory [and]</l>
<l rend="indent">the fierce victorious bird called Garuḍa, whose movement resembles the wind</l>
<l rend="indent">— all these surround and guard [Him]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
